        <updateDate>2020-09-16T18:14:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Leveraging Options for Counties And Localities Act or the LOCAL Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows payments from the Coronavirus Relief Fund, which were made to states, tribal governments, and local governments, to be used to cover expenditures incurred through December 31, 2021. Currently, expenditures must be incurred before December 31, 2020.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
